➜陶陶居飙汁手撕鸡！征服嘴刁老广…
http://www.sohu.com/a/421061905_100131509	46532
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200926/dc79159ec8ae45c3ad27298e3049f86c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200926/a979ec251eb245a097c52725cf61bdee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大多“为食又嘴刁”的老广</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">都会向一只有鸡味的鸡屈服</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">本加班狗也不例外</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但想在办公室<strong>方便快捷地吃到靓鸡</strong>，真难</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">直至我遇到了它…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/f3da4da79b5f4f91a54264793669f18e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
