<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/289ac65dbb734abdb44fe104adc2cf10.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200926/cd01c810ec9c49bc901926de366db2cd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200926/a0a7c79c067e4b419b1113d81cb24fd3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/在法律允许范围内活动解释权归品牌所有/</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/0aa8f90af57047b0bf366159411afea4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">广州是容纳来自五湖四海美食的食城</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但在这里，茶餐厅和粤菜的地位不可撼动</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>论和可口可乐谁最搭，TA们率先提名！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200926/30e1cbed6957417fbb5dffb381eff83c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“唔知食咩好，就表叔茶餐厅啦”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200926/3ba7ae5af733479d9876123cf1066f72.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200926/b33ab81aacbc4cb9a4527c791c5b0b00.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在广州，茶餐厅≈老广食堂，早餐直落宵夜都能全包。但自从<strong>可口可乐劲爽来袭</strong>，港奶在茶餐厅里的地位都不保了...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/87f42323e3e84e079d26a67cc396b550.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200926/0029add28ffd4a01a432f3c68538bf57.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每次去茶餐厅必点冻柠乐。菜还没上齐，就要先嘬上两口可口可乐，咕噜噜下肚，<strong>爽意上涌，胃口全开</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>五香牛杂 &amp; 烧腊拼盘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>//</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200926/b97f3c2b4e7145669c5ac4eaffd4d7c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200926/78603fc6e896430298e73a49656b68d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>吃小吃，就该搭可口可乐润润喉</strong>。牛杂分量实在，绵软细腻，超惹味。「港式烧味拼盘」让你过足烧腊瘾，叉烧、烧肉、豉油鸡、白切鸡、烧鹅一碟全包。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>干炒牛河</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200926/b9c17668abe34241b288d6d5802c4b30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200926/b1e5409e712a4460a511974b866034fc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">干炒牛河+可口可乐的搭配承包了很多老广的宵夜记忆。勐火快炒的牛河爽滑弹牙，充满油脂香气，冰爽的可口可乐又能<strong>让口腔瞬间恢复清新</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>冰火菠萝油</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200926/72e64a25c50b43b6a794f3b8b6ab99f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200926/662a4a4d747049d09eb278f6549809be.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">香脆酥皮邂逅醇厚的黄油，加上可口可乐的加持，这份<strong>碳水的快乐瞬间加倍</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/1f893f91acc946518d0037f334904da6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200926/4217655a6f924f3fabcb9cc3245c782b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200926/b14e55bf5e7f4afca390fa45399fcdd4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
